<h2 id="how-to-install-vtk">How to install VTK</h2>

<p>Download source file from <a href="https://vtk.org/download/">here</a></p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-xf</span> VTK-8.2.0.tar.gz
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">cd </span>VTK-8.2.0 <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="nb">mkdir </span>build <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="nb">cd </span>build
<span class="nv">$ </span>cmake ..
<span class="nv">$ </span>make                                                                   
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>make <span class="nb">install</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>ldconfig
</code></pre></div></div>

